orcSerDe.description: Nested argument that specifies converting data to the ORC format before storing it in Amazon S3. For more information, see [Apache ORC](https://orc.apache.org/docs/). More details below.

parquetSerDe.description: Nested argument that specifies converting data to the Parquet format before storing it in Amazon S3. For more information, see [Apache Parquet](https://parquet.apache.org/documentation/latest/). More details below.
